" <div class=\"graphic\">",
"  <div class=\"figure\" style=\"width: 470px\">",
"   <div class=\"ttl\">",
"    Cutaneous reactions to kissing bug bites",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 318px; height: 432px; background-image: url(data:image/jpeg;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    Cutaneous reactions consisting of erythema and edema may develop at the site of kissing bug bites.",
"    <div class=\"footnotes\">",
